{\*\cs24\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177 }.  The applicant\'92s understanding of convenience did not, it appeared, even extend to the question of
